title: Google\Cloud\Compute\V1\AllocationSpecificSKUAllocationReservedInstanceProperties\MaintenanceInterval
name: MaintenanceInterval
description:
Specifies whether this VM may be a stable fleet VM. Setting this to "Periodic" designates this VM as a Stable Fleet VM.

See go/stable-fleet-ug for more details.

Protobuf type google.cloud.compute.v1.AllocationSpecificSKUAllocationReservedInstanceProperties.MaintenanceInterval
